title: Chap's AMV Collection v2
description:
A moderate collection of AMVs, acquired between 2011 and early 2014. Not sorted, though collection has been curated for consistency, and most files are the highest quality which could be located. This is meant to replace the original release from about a year ago.   

Includes: 

-297 AMVs from around the internet
-AMV Hell Championship Collection 
-Fluximation
-Genius Party
-Genius Party Beyond
